  <title xml:lang="EN">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Increasing Governance Effectiveness in Vietnam through the Open Government Partnership Initiative</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1" xml:lang="EN">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">This project aims at enabling Vietnamese key anti-corruption agencies to expose to and learn from anti-corruption international experiences under the framework of the 18th International Anti-corruption Conference (IACC). This will help contribute to improving Vietnam&#x2019;s corruption efforts in the long run. 
Specific Objectives
Key Vietnamese anti-corruption agencies responsible for developing and implementing anti-corruption legislation will gain international experiences and practices in the relevant topics, such as : 
&#x2022;	Assets declaration and management.
&#x2022;	Handling corruption in business activities (both private to public and private-to private corruption) for promoting business integrity in Vietnam.</narrative>
  </description>
